INSTALLATION
============

Juomapeli requires following programs/stuff to work:

	aplay (alsa sample player)
	poissonrun - http://zakalwe.fi/~shd/foss/poissonrun/
	Python interpreter

	Something to drink...

USAGE EXAMPLE
=============

Two players, drink once every ten seconds in average (may happen more often
since this is a poisson random process):

$ juomapeli.sh 10 "kirk johnson" "bob goatse"
